author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Hardwood floor protection tips…I’m using Ram Board to protect these floors from paint and dust. The green Edge Tape secures boards to the hardwood without leaving behind residue. I use Seam Tape between boards because it’ll block liquids and debris. Definitely worth the time and effort to keep nice floors looking good.
